host_tracking_history.name: Hassan
host_tracking_history.about_text: My work: French teacher ; What makes my home unique: Always clean, quiet, welcoming. ; Pets: My Trail motorcycle. ; Where I went to school: Lycée Tarik Azrou, ENS Meknès, Fac casa. ; I spend too much time: Motorcycling and travel. ; Favorite song in high school: Imagine. John Lennon. ; I’m obsessed with: Good company, a good table. ; Speaks Arabic, English, and French ; Lives in Tangier, Morocco ; What's for breakfast: mint tea, tajine khli"3 with egg
host_tracking_history.bio_text: Epicurean in person, as I live alone, I am free in my movements and my lifestyle is more flexible. I travel whenever possible, most often with my biker buddies. Every year, we go to Faro in Portugal, Andalusia and deep Morocco.

reviews.name: Hassan
reviews.text: Thank you very much to Hassan for his wonderful welcome and the excellent stay I had in his house. Hassan is a very cultured man, full of resources. Very attentive, helpful, he seeks the well-being of others and puts you at ease. I rested well in peace while enjoying Tangier serenely. I intend to go back. Good places should be kept. I would highly recommend it.

reviews.name: Hassan
reviews.text:
My experience with Mr. Hassan was truly exceptional. He is one of the most respectful and kind individuals I have ever dealt with. His warm and welcoming attitude made us feel right at home.
The apartment he offers is excellent in every aspect — extremely clean, well-organized, and ideally located with all necessary services nearby.
I highly recommend staying at his place, and I am certain this will not be the last time we choose to deal with him

reviews.name: Hassan
reviews.text: Thank you very much Mr. Hassan

reviews.name: Hassan
reviews.text: Hassan is very kind and polite, very well maintained and clean accommodation, with everything you need

reviews.name: Hassan
reviews.text: A big thank you to Hassan for hosting us and for his exceptional responsiveness throughout my stay. From the time of booking, he was very available by phone, always ready to guide me and answer all my questions with kindness. The accommodation was impeccable: very clean, well maintained, and exactly as described. The location is ideal, easily accessible by public transport, with all the shops and very good places to eat a stone's throw away. It was a real pleasure to stay here, I highly recommend this place to anyone looking to have a good time in Tangier. Congratulations to Hassan for his professionalism, his sense of service and the quality of his accommodation!
